---
title: Breaded Baked Chicken with Buttery Rice, Zucchini and Lemony Mayo
description: Crunchy golden breadcrumbs make this baked chicken a breeze to whip up! Our DIY lemony mayo is a delicious dipper and the perfect finish to this weeknight winner.
